  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Keeping careful eye on an area, you prepare to take a shot at any enemy that appears. The area that you can overwatch is a cone with double your weapon's range. Set this area when you use this action. There cannot be any visible enemies in this cone when it is set. Until the start of your next turn, you can spend a reaction to attempt a Strike with your readied ranged weapon at any target that you see in this area. If you use this ability again, it allows you to set a new cone and you are no longer watching the previous cone.</p>",
